The paper also proposes a new attentive module in deep neural network, which falls under the category of ML algorithms and architectures, making cs.MM (Multimedia) another likely sub-category. The paper also involves training and optimizing deep neural networks, which falls under the category of ML algorithms and architectures, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of attention mechanisms, which falls under the category of AI and reasoning, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely sub-category. Finally, the paper involves image retrieval and classification, which falls under the category of information retrieval, making cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely sub-category.
